s.\\n\\n\\nCare Tip - Just keep it away from too much water. And if it gets a little dusty, give it a gentle dusting every now and then with a soft cloth, and it'll keep looking awesome.", "inventory_id": "IN0035"}, "mid_code": null, "subtitle": null, "thumbnail": "https://backend.theblissfulsoul.in/static/1776424258417-IN0035.png", "collection": {"id": "pcol_01KNVKGSH7VX6P46MTFH11MMFM"}, "created_at": "2026-04-17T11:10:58.535Z", "deleted_at": null, "updated_at": "2026-04-17T11:15:58.343Z", "description": "Introducing our Pyrite Clusters (Set of 4) a small yet mighty charm that invites abundance, prosperity, and positivity into your life, whether it graces your home, office, or any key you attach it to. Crafted from the captivating mineral known as pyrite, this keychain is more than just an accessory; it's a symbol of strength and wealth. Pyrite, also known as \\"Fool's Gold,\\" has long been revered for its metaphysical properties.\\n\\nCarry our Pyrite Keyring with you wherever you go, and let its powerful presence amplify your intentions for success and prosperity. Whether adorning your keyring or adorning your space, this keychain serves as a constant reminder of the abundance that surrounds you, waiting to be claimed.\\n\\nTransform your everyday routine into a magnet for good fortune with our Pyrite Keychain.\\n\\nKindly Note That images are just a graphical representation of crystals. Size, Shape and Colour may vary at the time of delivery.\\n\\n---\\n\\nOur Pyrite Clusters consist of 4 pieces - a small, shiny treasure from the Earth to inspire confidence, enhance willpower, and promote a sense of abundance.\\n\\n---\\n\\nNature Excellence - Our Pyrite Clusters are sourced with care, ensuring the quality and authenticity of each piece. Each cluster is a unique composition of golden hues, showcasing the raw allure of pyrite.\\nVersatile - Pyrite Cluster on your crystal altar for manifestation rituals, meditation, or in a home office for enhanced focus and conf