prod_01KPDJ5M0N21GRTZ6AHPQNJT69	Citrine Bracelet	in0006	\N	The Crystal of Success, Sunshine & Manifestation\n\nCitrine is cherished across the world as the Crystal of Success — a crystal that inspires growth, progress, and radiant positivity. Its warm golden glow is believed to carry the energy of the sun, making it a symbol of light, vitality, and joy. Wherever Citrine is placed or worn, it is said to dissolve the shadows of doubt and fear, replacing them with confidence and enthusiasm to chase your dreams.\n\nFor centuries, traders and merchants kept Citrine in their cash boxes, treasuries, and places of business to attract wealth and consistent financial flow, which led to its famed title — The Merchant’s Crystal. It is thought to amplify intentions and help manifest goals faster, making it a favorite for achievers, entrepreneurs, and those beginning new chapters in life.\n\n---\n\n1. Jewellery Type\nElegant Citrine crystal bracelet\n\n2. Minimalist Design\nSimple, clean look with warm golden tones\n\n3. Handcrafted Piece\nCarefully made with natural crystals\n\n4. Comfortable Fit\nLightweight and easy for everyday wear\n\n---\n\nMade with 100% natural Citrine crystal beads, known for their vibrant golden hue and energy of abundance.\nEach bead is carefully polished and hand-strung to preserve its natural power and shine.	f	published	https://backend.pragyavijh.com/static/1776424243100-IN0006.png	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	2026-04-17 11:10:43.222+00	2026-04-17 11:10:43.222+00	\N	{"ingredients": "Made with 100% natural Citrine crystal beads, known for their vibrant golden hue and energy of abundance.\\nEach bead is carefully polished and hand-strung to preserve its natural power and shine.", "inventory_id": "IN0006"}
