prod_01KPDJ62Z60Z5MY9VQS2XHTVZX	Pyrite Clusters ( set of 4)	in0035	\N	Introducing our Pyrite Clusters (Set of 4) a small yet mighty charm that invites abundance, prosperity, and positivity into your life, whether it graces your home, office, or any key you attach it to. Crafted from the captivating mineral known as pyrite, this keychain is more than just an accessory; it's a symbol of strength and wealth. Pyrite, also known as "Fool's Gold," has long been revered for its metaphysical properties.\n\nCarry our Pyrite Keyring with you wherever you go, and let its powerful presence amplify your intentions for success and prosperity. Whether adorning your keyring or adorning your space, this keychain serves as a constant reminder of the abundance that surrounds you, waiting to be claimed.\n\nTransform your everyday routine into a magnet for good fortune with our Pyrite Keychain.\n\nKindly Note That images are just a graphical representation of crystals. Size, Shape and Colour may vary at the time of delivery.\n\n---\n\nOur Pyrite Clusters consist of 4 pieces - a small, shiny treasure from the Earth to inspire confidence, enhance willpower, and promote a sense of abundance.\n\n---\n\nNature Excellence - Our Pyrite Clusters are sourced with care, ensuring the quality and authenticity of each piece. Each cluster is a unique composition of golden hues, showcasing the raw allure of pyrite.\nVersatile - Pyrite Cluster on your crystal altar for manifestation rituals, meditation, or in a home office for enhanced focus and confidence. Its compact size allows for versatile use, bringing the empowering and grounding energies to any space.\nPyrite, often called "Fool's Gold," is believed to attract prosperity and abundance, making this cluster not just a beautiful addition to your space but also a symbol of your intentions for success.\n\n\nCare Tip - Just keep it away from too much water. And if it gets a little dusty, give it a gentle dusting every now and then with a soft cloth, and it'll keep looking awesome.	f	published	https://backend.pragyavijh.com/static/1776424258417-IN0035.png	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	pcol_01KNVKGSH7VX6P46MTFH11MMFM	\N	t	\N	2026-04-17 11:10:58.535+00	2026-04-17 11:15:58.343+00	\N	{"ingredients": "Nature Excellence - Our Pyrite Clusters are sourced with care, ensuring the quality and authenticity of each piece. Each cluster is a unique composition of golden hues, showcasing the raw allure of pyrite.\\nVersatile - Pyrite Cluster on your crystal altar for manifestation rituals, meditation, or in a home office for enhanced focus and confidence. Its compact size allows for versatile use, bringing the empowering and grounding energies to any space.\\nPyrite, often called \\"Fool's Gold,\\" is believed to attract prosperity and abundance, making this cluster not just a beautiful addition to your space but also a symbol of your intentions for success.\\n\\n\\nCare Tip - Just keep it away from too much water. And if it gets a little dusty, give it a gentle dusting every now and then with a soft cloth, and it'll keep looking awesome.", "inventory_id": "IN0035"}
prod_01KPDJ5YHHN4Y71S80X7CBXCJN	Rose Quartz Tumbles	in0027	\N	Experience love's transformative power with our beautiful Rose Quartz Pencil Pendant. Handcrafted from genuine rose quartz crystals, this stunning piece radiates healing energy. Embrace self-love, attract positive relationships, and find emotional balance with the soothing energy of rose quartz.\n\nRose quartz, known as the stone of unconditional love, is renowned for its gentle pink hue and powerful healing properties. It supports emotional healing, fosters harmonious relationships, and encourages self-love.\n\nNOTE: Kindly note that images are just a graphical representation of crystals. Size, Shape and Colour may vary at the time of delivery.\n\n---\n\n✤Promote unconditional love and compassion.\n✤Enhance feelings of self-love and acceptance.\n✤It can help attract and strengthen romantic relationships.\n✤Rose quartz is believed to bring peace, harmony, and a sense of calmness.\n\n---\n\nRose Quartz Crystal is formed by magma crystallization. As the magma cools, it causes some elements and minerals to become purified and others to bond together. Silicon mixes with oxygen and begins to form a quartz crystal.	f	published	https://backend.pragyavijh.com/static/1776424253836-IN0027.png	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	pcol_01KNVHDH2YA8S5AMDR1P6VNT4R	\N	t	\N	2026-04-17 11:10:54.002+00	2026-04-17 11:15:18.346+00	\N	{"ingredients": "Rose Quartz Crystal is formed by magma crystallization. As the magma cools, it causes some elements and minerals to become purified and others to bond together. Silicon mixes with oxygen and begins to form a quartz crystal.", "inventory_id": "IN0027"}
prod_01KPDJ5XZSSBBZKRAYAJ09M268	Amethyst Locket	in0026	\N	If you're starting your crystal healing journey, Amethyst is a great starting point. It's the crystal of alignment and balance.\n\nKnown as "The All-Purpose Stone", Amethyst is a protective stone that helps to relieve stress and anxiety in your life. One of the most effective ways to detoxify the body using amethyst is to place a large amethyst geode in a room where you spend a lot of time so that your body can be surrounded by its cleansing energies on a regular basis.\n\nKindly Note That images are just a graphical representation of crystals. Size, Shape and Colour may vary at the time of delivery.\n\n---\n\nAmethyst can help promote calmness and relaxation.\nIt aid in reducing stress and anxiety.\nIt can assist in promoting a good night's sleep.\nIt may help with addictive behaviors and negative thought patterns.\n\n---\n\nAmethyst crystals are formed naturally from a combination of silicon dioxide and iron impurities in the presence of heat and pressure, over time creating purple-colored crystals in rock cavities.\n\nNOTE: These naturally occurring crystals have been shaped to make this pencil pendant keeping their natural cuts, and fissures in place. We haven’t excessively polished them so you may have pieces that have natural fissures in them.	f	published	https://backend.pragyavijh.com/static/1776424253315-IN0026.png	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	pcol_01KNVHDH2YA8S5AMDR1P6VNT4R	\N	t	\N	2026-04-17 11:10:53.433+00	2026-04-17 11:15:18.346+00	\N	{"ingredients": "Amethyst crystals are formed naturally from a combination of silicon dioxide and iron impurities in the presence of heat and pressure, over time creating purple-colored crystals in rock cavities.\\n\\nNOTE: These naturally occurring crystals have been shaped to make this pencil pendant keeping their natural cuts, and fissures in place. We haven’t excessively polished them so you may have pieces that have natural fissures in them.", "inventory_id": "IN0026